\{T_\alpha\}_{\alpha \in \mathcal{A}} \subset \mathcal{B}(X)
X
x \in X\setminus \{0\}
M_x>0
\|T_\alpha x\| \geq M_x ,\ \forall \alpha \in \mathcal{A}
M>0
\|T_\alpha\| \geq M
T
x \neq 0
 \| T \| := \sup_{\|x\| = 1} |T \; x| 
 \| T_{\alpha} x \| \ge M_x 
 \| T_{\alpha} \| \ge \left| T\Big(\frac{x}{\| x \|} \Big) \right| \ge \frac{M_x}{\| x \|} 
